Text: More coming up as i download them... (100000 pics at the time)
People really don't think before they upload their shit...

And we're supposed to download a 24 GB zip file? 

Previews, samples and smaller files would help the bandwidth challenged among us.

I've just looked through the first 600 images on that site... and there was only maybe 1 halfway "win" image of a halfway decent looking lady in a bra.

The rest are number images of WoW, puppies, random people, sports stats, flags, etc.

Major waste of time and hard drive space.
